name: Green and Hot Pink - Braided Ribbon Barrettes
description:
As seen on LikeTotally80s.com.

These braided ribbon barrettes (green and hot pink) are one of the most requested ribbon color combinations I have had from previous buyers. Also, this ribbon color combination is one of the most popular colors from the 1980s. They are perfect for everyday wear and they would add a splash of color to your (or your daughter's) hair.

The color of the ribbons are:
- Green
- Hot Pink

Perfect for any woman/girl who has shoulder hair length and also for all types of hair (thin to thick, straight to wavy to curl).

This listing is for two (2) "Green and Hot Pink" braided ribbon barrettes.

Metal barrette - 2 and half inches (65mm) long
Ribbon "tail" - 9 inches (22cm and 8mm) long

(The ribbon tails are heat sealed.)

++ CUSTOM ORDER INFO ++
Please let me know if you would like to have me make you this barrette to:
- match your hair length (short, shoulder, or long)
- change the ribbon tails' direction toward the front of your face instead of in the back.
- add the pony beads to the ribbon tails

You can contact me for more details.


All designs & photographs © Retroeighties 2006-2012.

WARNING: Choking Hazard - Small Parts. Not for Children under 3 yrs.
